ActOffice of the Superintendent of Financial Institutions Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Assessment of Pension Plans Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the ASSESSMENT OF PENSION PLANS REGULATIONS in order to (1) simplify the assessment process for plan administrators and the Office of the Superintendent of Financial Institutions; (2) eliminate assessments for certain terminated plans; and (3) correct the definition of "beneficiary".
